					<outline text="Update: Believe it or not I actually had lunch &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.flickr.com/photos/scriptingnews/3859719627/&quot;&gt;yesterday&lt;/a&gt; with Joe Hewitt, the developer of this app. I said that if Facebook wanted to compete with Twitter they needed a vastly simpler version of Facebook. Little did I know that 24 hours later I'd be looking at it." created="Thu, 27 Aug 2009 22:46:59 GMT"/>
