					<outline text="I think it's great. I know that Eric Woodward wanted to move on from tr.im and this gives him the opportunity to do that, but allows the community that's gathered around tr.im to continue." created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 19:14:01 GMT"/>
					<outline text="I am part of that community -- having build an application that gets a lot of use, and one that a lot of people want. To match Eric's generosity, I will release the app behind the 40twits site as open source. " created="Mon, 17 Aug 2009 19:14:32 GMT"/>
